public static void loadPluginOLDFORMAT(java.io.File f,
                                                  BaseConsole c,

Deprecated. Use the new plugin format. TODO: THIS WILL BE REMOVED IN VERSION 5.x.x

Loads plugin from File f, at location into BaseConsole c.
This plugin must be in the old format with a jar file, and another text file with the same name (case sensitive) containing all the classes in the jar file that extend ConsoleListener that wants to be added when the plugin is loaded.

Parameters:
f - the file
c - the BaseConsole
location - the location of the file
